dct_description_sm: Title from panel. "Plano publicado por CARTUR Ltda." Oriented with north toward left. Includes list of municipalities [alcaldías menores] and their boundaries. Includes indexes of points of interest and streets. Ancillary map: "Bogotá D.C. principales calles y avenidas". "Base cartográfica: © "Instituto Geográfico Agustín Codazzi". Other sources of infomation: D.A.N.E., D.A.P.M., index for roads and residential districts was obtained from Planeación Distrital and edited by Cartur.
